{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8MX9HuLH9kzLt2vxThXRn","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# src/modules/verify -- Story Verification Module\n     2→\n     3→Handles story verification, proof document parsing, black-box verifier agent orchestration,\n     4→and Docker environment management for isolated verification.\n     5→\n     6→## Module Structure\n     7→\n     8→| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n     9→|------|---------|-------------|\n    10→| index.ts | Public interface — delegates to internal files | `verifyStory`, `parseProof`, re-exports all public types/functions |\n    11→| orchestrator.ts | Verification pipeline orchestration | `checkPreconditions`, `createProofDocument`, `runShowboatVerify`, `updateVerificationState`, `closeBeadsIssue` |\n    12→| parser.ts | Story AC extraction and classification | `parseStoryACs`, `classifyAC`, `classifyVerifiability`, `classifyStrategy`, `parseVerificationTag` |\n    13→| proof.ts | Proof quality validation + black-box enforcement | `validateProofQuality`, `proofHasContent`, `classifyEvidenceCommands`, `checkBlackBoxEnforcement` |\n    14→| env.ts | Docker image lifecycle + clean workspace + stale container cleanup. Supports nodejs, python, rust, plugin, and generic project types. | `buildVerifyImage`, `prepareVerifyWorkspace`, `checkVerifyEnv`, `cleanupVerifyEnv`, `cleanupStaleContainers`, `isValidStoryKey`, `computeDistHash`, `detectProjectType` |\n    15→| browser.ts | Agent-browser integration for UI testing in Docker | `BrowserVerifier` class with `navigate`, `screenshot`, `click`, `type`, `evaluate`, `isAvailable`, `diffScreenshots` |\n    16→| types.ts | All verify domain types | `VerifyResult`, `ProofQuality`, `ParsedAC`, `BuildOptions`, `BuildResult`, `CheckResult`, `BrowserActionResult`, `DiffResult`, etc. |\n    17→| validation-acs.ts | Validation AC registry barrel — combines all 79 ACs | `VALIDATION_ACS`, `getACsByCategory`, `getCliVerifiableACs`, `getIntegrationRequiredACs`, `getACById` |\n    18→| validation-ac-types.ts | Types for validation AC entries | `ValidationAC`, `VerificationMethod`, `AcCategory` |\n    19→| validation-ac-fr.ts | FR validation AC data (ACs 1-40) | `FR_ACS` |\n    20→| validation-ac-data.ts | NFR/UX/Regression/ActionItem AC data (ACs 41-79) | `NFR_ACS`, `UX_ACS`, `REGRESSION_ACS`, `ACTION_ITEM_ACS` |\n    21→| validation-runner.ts | Validation infrastructure: sprint init, AC execution, fix story gen, result processing | `createValidationSprint`, `executeValidationAC`, `createFixStory`, `processValidationResult` |\n    22→| validation-orchestrator.ts | Validation orchestration: cycle execution, progress tracking | `runValidationCycle`, `getValidationProgress` |\n    23→| validation-runner-types.ts | Types for validation runner | `ValidationACResult`, `ValidationSprintResult`, `ValidationCycleResult`, `ValidationProgress`, `ValidationVerdict` |\n    24→\n    25→## Module Boundary\n    26→\n    27→Only `index.ts` should be imported from outside this module. Internal files (`orchestrator.ts`, `parser.ts`, `proof.ts`, `env.ts`) are not part of the public API.\n    28→\n    29→## Tests (`__tests__/`)\n    30→\n    31→| File | Tests For | Source Location |\n    32→|------|-----------|-----------------|\n    33→| index.test.ts | Module delegation (verifyStory, parseProof) | `./index.ts` |\n    34→| verify.test.ts | Orchestrator + proof quality validation | `./orchestrator.ts`, `./proof.ts` |\n    35→| verify-blackbox.test.ts | Black-box enforcement logic | `./proof.ts` |\n    36→| verify-prompt.test.ts | Verifier prompt generation | `src/templates/verify-prompt.ts` |\n    37→| verify-env.test.ts | Environment checks (Docker, workspace) | `./env.ts` |\n    38→| verify-parser.test.ts | Story AC parsing, classification | `./parser.ts` |\n    39→| verifier-session.test.ts | Verifier session management | `src/lib/verifier-session.ts` |\n    40→| browser.test.ts | BrowserVerifier unit tests (mocked docker exec) | `./browser.ts` |\n    41→| validation-acs.test.ts | Validation AC registry: count, structure, distribution, helpers | `./validation-acs.ts` |\n    42→| validation-runner.test.ts | Validation runner: sprint init, AC execution, fix stories, result processing, orchestration | `./validation-runner.ts`, `./validation-orchestrator.ts` |\n    43→| verification-observability-patch.test.ts | Patch content validation + observability integration regression tests | `patches/verify/story-verification.md`, `src/templates/verify-prompt.ts`, `./parser.ts` |\n    44→\n    45→## Architecture Notes\n    46→\n    47→- All public functions return `Result<T>` (via `verifyStory`, `parseProof`) or throw (legacy direct exports).\n    48→- Old `src/lib/verify.ts`, `src/lib/verify-parser.ts`, `src/lib/verify-env.ts` have been deleted.\n    49→- Commands (`src/commands/verify.ts`, `src/commands/verify-env.ts`, `src/commands/validate.ts`) import only from `./index.ts`.\n    50→- The `codeharness status` command imports `getValidationProgress` from `./index.ts` for real-time validation display.\n    51→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01UEcnB3h2gZqmEJqfPaXmt4","session_id":"38809bab-d371-4c03-b647-b7b7381ee002","uuid":"18f2b142-64c1-4f06-be9e-4eddba211716","timestamp":"2026-03-24T23:43:09.979Z"}
